  "translations": {
    "en": "Muhammad ibn Ali ibn al-Fadl al-Kufi (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Abu Ja'far Muhammad ibn Ammar al-Qattan narrated to us. He said: al-Husayn ibn Ali ibn al-Hakam al-Za'farani narrated to me. He said: Ismail ibn Ibrahim al-'Abdi narrated to us. He said: Sahl ibn Ziyad al-Adami narrated to me, from Ibn Mahbub, from Abu Hamza al-Thumali. He said:",
